An enum containing public-facing constants and setup methods.
The reason to use enums across Ribbons is to avoid instantiation and simulate namespaces..
Graphical component to render the average rating of a product using 5 stars and the number of ratings.
The rating is a floating point number between 0.0 and 5.0 (max number of stars). If the provided value is outside this range, it will be clamped.
The numberOfReviews is a positive integer number.
